# 默认：所有文本文件在工作区使用 CRLF
* text=auto eol=crlf

# （建议保留）这些文件最好还是 LF：避免以后你们用到 Docker/WSL/CI 或 Linux 时踩坑
*.sh text eol=lf
Dockerfile text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf

# 二进制文件：禁止换行符转换
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.7z  binary
*.rar binary
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
